        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="4091-e11a-c858-f46e">Field an 8.8cm Heavy AA Platoon (LG144) in place of an 8.8cm SS Heavy AA Platoon (LG227). This Unit has the following ratings for -1 point per Gun team:
MOTIVATIONCONFIDENT4+Family MenLast Stand 5+
