        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="fa11-60d9-4bb8-7538">If the Formation Commander is on table or in Reserve and Units of this Formation are in Reserve, re-roll one failed Reserves die.If successful, this die can only be used to bring a Unit from this Formation on from Reserves.</characteristic>
