      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="fa11-60d9-4bb8-7538">When this Unit is Destroyed, replace the Unit Leader with an Independent Infantry Team armed with Panzerfaust anti-tank weapons using the characteristics from SS-Panzergrenadier Company HQ (LG208).</characteristic>
