      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="fa11-60d9-4bb8-7538">The Unit Leader may re-roll one failed roll To Hit each time he Shoots with his 7.5cm gun.This Unit gains the Scout rule.Scout: Teams remain Gone to Ground while Moving unless they Shoot or Assault.</characteristic>
