      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="fa11-60d9-4bb8-7538">The Unit Leader may re-roll one failed roll To Hit in each Shooting Step.If the Unit Leader is Destroyed, roll a die. On a score of 5+, it is Bailed Out instead.</characteristic>
