  <profiles>
    <profile id="0aad-bac8-54cb-9c1e" name="Pakfront" hidden="false" typeId="c86b-12b3-c1b1-b8e0" typeName="Command Card [Revised]">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="fa11-60d9-4bb8-7538">Gun teams in this Unit cannot Move, but can rotate to face the target when Shooting, and are Nests.Each Gun team is a separate Independent Team.Nest: The Nests are always Concealed and in Bulletproof Cover.Teams attacking a Nest must re-roll successful Firepower tests to Destroy it.Nests cannot Charge into Contact.LFTF: This card can be used with any Gun Unit, including artillery and anti-aircraft guns. Units using this card cannot fire Artillery Bombardments or shoot at Aircraft. Pakfront Nests do not use the Beach Defences rules from the D-Day: American book.LFTF: This costs +2 points per Gun team, rather than +6 points for the Unit.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile id="beec-ce54-64f1-254e" name="Forces ID" typeId="86a9-a6ee-b9bd-dafe" typeName="Forces ID" hidden="false">
