  <profiles>
    <profile id="9787-e903-3b62-cf07" name="Machine-gun Nests" hidden="false" typeId="c86b-12b3-c1b1-b8e0" typeName="Command Card [Revised]">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="fa11-60d9-4bb8-7538">MG42 HMG teams in this Unit cannot Move, but can rotate to face the target when Shooting, and are Nests.Each HMG team is a separate Independent Team.Nest: The Nests are always Concealed and in Bulletproof Cover.Teams attacking a Nest must re-roll successful Firepower tests to Destroy it.Nests cannot Charge into Contact.</characteristic>
