      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="fa11-60d9-4bb8-7538">This 8.8cm Tank-hunter Platoon may fire an Artillery Bombardment with the following characteristics:
            
                WeaponRangeROF HaltedROF MovingAnti- tankFire- power
