  <profiles>
    <profile id="5d84-7f58-793c-052b" name="Old Minefields" hidden="false" typeId="c86b-12b3-c1b1-b8e0" typeName="Command Card [Revised]">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Details" typeId="fa11-60d9-4bb8-7538">Before Objectives are placed, place five Old Minefield markers. The players alternate placing markers, starting with this player. Markers must be placed in No-Man&apos;s Land or this Force&apos;s Deployment Area, and at least 4&quot;/10cm apart.When a Team moves within 2&quot;/5cm of an Old Minefield marker, roll a die. On a score of 4+, remove the Old Minefield marker. Otherwise, replace the Old Minefield marker with a Minefield Marker and test for entering a Minefield as normal.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile id="1bca-c766-0bcb-6f99" name="Forces ID" typeId="86a9-a6ee-b9bd-dafe" typeName="Forces ID" hidden="false">
